_sText:
fixed version of my map

high variety of traps, including a vent complex trap.

3 secrets, 3 end choices (old, bhop, knife) and a secret ending (3 secret buttons) which leads to awp and MG for old.

Again, any bugs/problems/improvements would be appreciated!

(p.s - a teleport has been put in for testing reasons on the left side at the start as you jump over the barrier. This skips to the final part of the level.)
